imdb.plot outline: Ever wondered how a Tour player thinks? What their strategy is? How, under pressure, they hit the shots that pull it all together?We take you inside the minds of our team of top Tour players and coaches to learn their inner thoughts on the best way to play each course, fine tune their games and discuss how to produce all of the successful shots.
